American Can Co said it plansto change its name to Primerica Corp, subject to approval byshareholders at the April 28 annual meeting.    It said its new New York Stock Exchange ticker symbol wouldbe &lt;PA>.    American Can sold all its packaging operations -- andrights to the American Can name -- to Triangle Industries Inc&lt;TRI> in November.    The company said the new name gives it flexibility as itmoves into new areas of enterprise.  American Can is nowinvolved in financial services and specialty retailing. Reuter&#3;